  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4ffa88ce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRY5pr2NgayiaHgAxhGJROeXs2t3Iia1SP70h675zABXYPv6hgSnESEoaYw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;caret-color:rgb(34, 34, 34);outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;text-shadow:transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility:visible;color:rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:27.2px;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n    <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n     <div data-id=\"85660\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n      <div data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 2em; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right-style: none; border-left-style: none; text-decoration: inherit; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 2em;padding-top: 0.5em;padding-bottom: 0.5em;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-right-style: none;border-left-style: none;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n       <p mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: -1.2em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; text-align: center; font-family: inherit; border-width: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 29.75px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: -1.2em;outline: 0px;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;text-align: center;font-family: inherit;border-width: initial;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 29.75px;\"><span mp-original-font-size=\"15\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-color:rgb(117, 117, 118);outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:15px;font-family:inherit;line-height:29.75px;\"><span leaf=\"\">机器之心报道</span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: center;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">机器之心编辑部</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">说出概念，SAM 3 就明白你在说什么，并在所有出现的位置精确描绘出边界。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Meta 的「分割一切」再上新？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">9 月 12 日，一篇匿名论文「SAM 3: SEGMENT ANYTHING WITH CONCEPTS」登陆 ICLR 2026，引发网友广泛关注。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511405\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7095709570957096\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1818\" data-width=\"1818\" data-height=\"1290\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8b1550a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYSj5EoxNCJY829wuP3OfapZTmRNhe0LOHq7lPq9V09h1RrWrGHRet1w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文标题：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">SAM 3: Segment Anything with Concepts</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文地址：<a href=\"https://openreview.net/forum?id=r35clVtGzw\" target=\"_blank\">https://openreview.net/forum?id=r35clVtGzw</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大家纷纷猜测，这篇论文出自 Meta，毕竟文风和 Meta 以前发布的论文非常相似。再加上 SAM 与 SAM 2 均由 Meta 推出，这让外界几乎可以确定，SAM 3 就是 Meta「Segment Anything」系列的正式续作。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511406\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24745762711864408\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"885\" data-width=\"885\" data-height=\"219\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=19296200&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYUnibicR4IUcon1h0EuFUo3pPrIWuQDvyib6pUAqmFjLibN9IS4OHRfCMbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在时间节点上，这篇论文的出现也几乎完美契合 Meta 的节奏。SAM 1 于&nbsp;</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&amp;mid=2650872938&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=ddb938b9c7e6206a0b97032cb9dee30a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"2023 年 4 月发表\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2023 年 4 月发表</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，获得当年 ICCV 最佳论文提名，其（零样本）分割一切的概念让研究者直呼「CV」不存在了，并且被誉为 CV 领域的「GPT-3 时刻」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&amp;mid=2650928134&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7855c453083236c5c5d121d3b4fb955e&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"SAM 2 于 2024 年 7 月发表\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SAM 2 于 2024 年 7 月发表</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，在前身的基础上为静态图像和动态视频内容提供实时、可提示的对象分割，将图像和视频分割功能统一到一个强大的系统中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而如今，又是一年过去了。SAM 3 的登场似乎恰逢其时。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">那么这次 SAM 3 有什么新进展呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它被定义为一个更高级的任务：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">可</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">提示概念分割（Pr</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">omptable Concept Segmentation, PCS）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">即将文本和 / 或图像范例作为输入，为每一个与该概念匹配的对象预测实例掩码和语义掩码，同时在视频帧之间保持对象身份的一致性。该工作的重点是识别原子视觉概念 (atomic visual concepts)，因此</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">将输入文本限制为简单的名词短语，例如「红苹果」或「条纹猫」，只要描述你想要的东西，它就能在图像或视频中找到并分割出每一个对应实例</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这意味着，分割终于学会了理解语言，但不是那种模糊的语义联想，而是一种扎根于视觉的极简理解方式。说出概念，它就明白你在说什么，并在所有出现的位置精确描绘出边界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有的小伙伴可能记得，SAM 1 就有文本功能，这次又有什么不同呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">论文中明确指出，在 SAM 1 中，文本提示的功能「没有被完全开发」（were not fully developed）。SAM 1 和 SAM 2 的实际重点在于</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">视觉提示</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（如点、框、掩码）。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511409\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1814814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1125\" data-height=\"204\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8aea1fe9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYtKtg0wbWKYBZbqX5ocsP0WA4xQc5qfvIRhCJ1d3e5oDMWnEVBsLV8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它们未能解决一个更广泛的任务：即找到并分割出输入内容中（例如，一段视频里所有的「猫」）出现的某一概念的所有实例。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511410\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1175925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1121\" data-height=\"132\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2b6f630&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYTMEOctFlJ1wQz8fBnQUkU5a91kIroaymjTr9CAQHSEOhicjnVdJicRaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">简单来说，SAM 3 让用户从「手动一个个点出来」升级到了「告诉模型一个概念，它帮你全部找出来」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511411\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3194444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2957\" data-height=\"945\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7250b2f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYVVGLeTtxTwzbBdJQQkDV1lI2XukFRIpcEQKSb1ZniajkA0DRSMZBqFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">SAM3 在两方面均取得进步。在通过点击进行可提示视觉分割方面（左图），SAM3 的性能优于 SAM2；同时，它在可提示概念分割方面（右图）也取得了进展，用户可以通过一个简短的名词短语、图像范例或两者的组合，来指定一个视觉概念并分割出其所有实例。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在论文提出的新基准 SA-Co 上，SAM 3 的性能比之前的系统提升了至少 2 倍 。在多个公开基准测试上取得了 SOTA 成绩。例如，在 LVIS 数据集上，它的零样本掩码平均精度达到了 47.0，而之前的最佳纪录是 38.5 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时，模型在单个 H200 GPU 上处理一张有超过 100 个物体的图像仅需 30 毫秒 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不过评论区也对该工作提出了质疑。有人指出，根据文本描述分割物体的想法并不新鲜，在学术界早已被称为「指代分割」，并且已有相当多的研究。因此，有人认为这项工作只是将一个旧概念「重新命名」和包装。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511412\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6430976430976431\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"891\" data-width=\"891\" data-height=\"573\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8958cdd5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYicOH8UdcQSFZsNSXOkVmtbG8N9rVcEjIYYeUugyBU988nxRTuJiau5iaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">还有评论认为，Meta 只是在「追赶」开源社区的步伐，因为社区早已通过组合不同的模型（例如，将检测模型与 LLM API 结合）实现了类似的功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511413\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5218855218855218\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"891\" data-width=\"891\" data-height=\"465\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9bee3556&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRY8waaxcjkxiakWvUTXdra3biah1SSyDnHBPlfuFwASApLEiblZq5Tr5CCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">方法介绍</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;SRv1dsK3eoJHDhxoBQccHJLhncc&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;（一级）方法介绍&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+8&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;6923214627635462148&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;ae5e76d7-6afc-4cc8-bba4-83502c3a68be&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:66,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:8},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;CH0qdjcFBoabp0xaY9Ncaq0OnHg&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">文中提到，SAM 3 是对 SAM 2 的扩展，其在图像与视频中实现了可提示分割（promptable segmentation）的重大突破。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">与 SAM 2 相比，SAM 3 在可提示视觉分割（Promptable Visual Segmentation，PVS）上表现更优，并为可提示概念分割（Promptable Concept Segmentation，PCS）设定了新的标准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">至于 PCS 任务以及 PVS 任务，简单来说就是，SAM 3 接收概念提示（如简单的名词短语如黄色校车、图像示例）或视觉提示（如点、框、掩码）来定义需要进行时空分割的对象（可逐个分割）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">可以说，本文聚焦的重点是识别原子级视觉概念，如红色苹果（red apple）或条纹猫。如图 1 所示，用户可通过简短名词短语、图像示例或二者组合，分割指定视觉概念的所有实例。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511414\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39166666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1263\" data-height=\"495\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=99011e96&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYdzBh9ibQt33YCJf726HwldrwJAPwfIkcQdvYJfD1ibWHQOvOXeqLkSfQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不过 PCS 本身存在固有模糊性，许多概念具有多重释义：例如小窗户这个短语就很有主观性（多大算小？多大算大？）和边界模糊（是否包含百叶窗？）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">针对这一问题，Meta 在数据收集、指标设计和模型训练等多个阶段对这些模糊性问题进行了系统化处理。与前代 SAM 版本一致，SAM 3 保持完全交互性，允许用户通过添加优化提示来消除歧义，引导模型生成预期输出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在模型架构上，SAM 3 采用双编码器 - 解码器 Transformer 架构，这是一个具有图像级识别能力的检测器 —— 通过与跟踪器和内存模块相结合，可应用于视频领域。检测器和跟踪器通过对齐的感知编码器（PE）主干网络接收视觉 - 语言输入。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511415\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3611111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1170\" data-height=\"423\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=56324fbb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYPLHPYlN7IclichkiahPAMxjk4MDYGCibAPAddwTicP0lVYeyktnXqdtpicg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，该研究还构建了一个可扩展的人机协同数据引擎（如下图），用于为大规模多样化训练数据集进行标注。基于这套系统，该研究成功标注了包含 400 万独特短语和 5200 万掩码的高质量训练数据，以及包含 3800 万短语和 14 亿掩码的合成数据集。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511416\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3814814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1266\" data-height=\"483\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=868eec5d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYGGNbBseyy19ZzngQtTngUe0xUYx5PEEoC7l2up0KTgej1XpvRZ0L7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更进一步的，本文还创建了用于 PCS 任务的 Segment Anything with Concepts（SA-Co）基准测试，涵盖 124K 张图像和 1.7K 视频中的 214K 独特概念，其概念数量超过现有基准测试集 50 倍以上。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511417\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5324074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1245\" data-height=\"663\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=95a07f78&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYT42IapoUNJ0ohBJx8AKbPrPK1rUiawenvwqZ49zrBoRVZNoPGquyAyA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">实验</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;SRv1dsK3eoJHDhxoBQccHJLhncc&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;（一级）实验&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+6&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;6923214627635462148&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;1b95e411-358d-4007-b745-a4b860d94ae1&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:108,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:6},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;RQX4dZh2moX2hmxcYzTcDfS6n0g&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">表 1 显示：在零样本设置下，SAM 3 在封闭词汇数据集 COCO、COCO-O 和 LVIS 的边界框检测任务中具有竞争力，在 LVIS 掩码任务上表现显著更好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在开放词汇 SA-Co/Gold 数据集上，SAM 3 的 CGF 分数是最强基线 OWLv2 的两倍，在其他 SA-Co 子集上的提升甚至更高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 ADE-847、PascalConcept-59 和 Cityscapes 上进行的开放词汇语义分割实验显示，SAM 3 的表现超越了强大的专家型基线 APE。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511418\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3888888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1614\" data-height=\"627\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=312265f9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYx7XtSRApwYrXajBDIviaZZDMOHqLVianKbElnpNWUL0ic4NLNBPYglV8w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小样本自适应。SAM 3 在 10-shot 设置下实现了当前最优性能，超过了 Gemini 的上下文提示以及目标检测专家模型（如 gDino）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">带有 1 个样本的 PCS。表 3 显示在三种设置下，SAM 3 在 COCO (+17.2)、LVIS (+9.7) 和 ODinW (+20.1) 上的表现均远超之前最先进的 T-Rex2。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511419\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22962962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1217\" data-height=\"279\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=221dc8e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYYwkDW348B9uia2s2bncup7k4FHGCMfCbwR7mvjibUxXibn14v2YmKgJhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">物体计数。结果如表 4 所示，与 MLLM 相比，SAM 3 不仅实现了良好的物体计数准确率，而且还提供了大多数 MLLM 无法提供的对象分割功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"387\" data-imgfileid=\"503511420\" data-ratio=\"0.5201612903225806\" data-width=\"744\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"744\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9fd5cce3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYWibM9zFrCeZccmK9LHLomzG19dgMibgic7xsKzE5n6LYDNKrfRUwLjTIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SAM 3 在文本提示下的视频分割表现。结果显示 SAM 3 的表现远超基线，尤其是在包含大量名词短语的基准测试中。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"605\" data-imgfileid=\"503511421\" data-ratio=\"0.37407407407407406\" data-width=\"1617\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c41481cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYFibibunsCbnlAtlU0NgibddsuMrxhuZbMKmpuSibib7ySSFicLcvdIOJSVbg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">表 6 将 SAM 3 与 VOS（Video Object Segmentation） 任务上的先进方法进行了比较。SAM 3 在大多数基准测试中都比 SAM 2 取得了显著的改进。对于交互式图像分割任务，SAM 3 在平均 mIoU 方面优于 SAM 2。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503511422\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24351851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1341\" data-height=\"326\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ef1fe654&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8femVrafGpgjqs6Z5pbJRYWgtqXn0GqqGqdvQiaJlZv7amYkRJBZp8AvWhMfYRVib4u3V22WJMfL0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">了解更多内容，请参考原论文。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "SAM 3 引入可提示概念分割，让模型通过文本/图像概念理解并分割所有对应实例，显著提升了图像和视频分割能力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "SAM 3 引入可提示概念分割，让模型通过文本/图像概念理解并分割所有对应实例，显著提升了图像和视频分割能力。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了疑似 Meta 推出的匿名论文《SAM 3: SEGMENT ANYTHING WITH CONCEPTS》，该论文已提交至 ICLR 2026，其核心创新是引入“可提示概念分割”（PCS）任务。SAM 3 允许用户通过简单的文本短语或图像范例来指定视觉概念（如“红苹果”），模型便能在图像或视频中识别并分割出该概念的所有实例，解决了前代 SAM 模型在文本提示功能上的不足。新模型在多项基准测试（如 SA-Co、LVIS）上取得了 SOTA 性能，在图像和视频分割能力上均有显著提升，且处理速度快。文章还探讨了 SAM 3 在模糊概念处理、模型架构（双编码器-解码器 Transformer）和大规模数据标注（SA-Co 基准）方面的进展。尽管有观点认为其与现有“指代分割”概念类似，且开源社区已实现类似功能，但 SAM 3 在性能和统一性上仍展现了显著优势。",
